{
  "texts": [
    "Defining such a transformation a priori exactly for all possible inputs is quasi-impossible, which is why current methods of artificial intelligence take the detour of estimating such a transformation based on given examples.",
    "The language used for this in AI is generally mathematics.",
    "The starting point is a flexible representation of this sought-after mathematical transformation, which can take various forms by setting different free parameters.",
    "Let's take the sentence \"I'm feeling good today\" as an example.",
    "If the word good is assigned a high weighting, this sentence could be regarded as rather positive."
  ]
}